So here's my little report type thing for this past friday.&nbsp; Ended up having four calls, first was an RMA for a girl who had passed out, apparently from cold medicine.&nbsp; Second wasan old lady who had just gotten out of the hospital that we had to bring back in cause she was vomiting.&nbsp; Third was my first overdose/suicide.&nbsp; 

It was rainging pretty badly by the time that one came around, so I got pretty wet.&nbsp; The medics on this one were real assholes too, the guy that was in the back with Brian and me was really rude, both to us and to the patient.&nbsp; When we got to RBMC the female on pushed the patient out of the way(ont he cot) so she could get to the admitting counter.&nbsp; 

Last was a "stabbing", and I use quotes around that because that's how the call came in, but the guy pretty much had a paper cut.&nbsp; It was three tiny slashes on his stomach that wasn't even bleeding byt het ime we got there.&nbsp; Plus his story didn't add up and I think the PD were thinking the same thing.

So after we were pretty much done for the night a bunch of us popped in Forrest Gump.&nbsp; Twas a good time had by all.
